    "description": "Nutanix Flow Security Central helps you keep your hybrid cloud safe across Amazon Web Services, Microsoft Azure and Nutanix Private Cloud. Identify and fix security issues in real-time. Automate compliance checks for cloud operations using 550+ audits. Get compliance checks for regulatory policies such as HIPAA, PCI-DSS, NIST, and more.This add-on helps you integrate your Splunk install with your Beam account. It will bring all the Beam logs related to vulnerabilities detected and issue state changes to your Splunk install.",
